-- HSBC’s Qu Hongbin Says Yuan Band Widening Ends RMB Appreciation
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-04-14T06:28:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-14/hsbc-s-qu-hongbin-says-yuan-band-widening-ends-rmb-appreciation.html
Qu Hongbin, chief economist for
 China  at HSBC Holdings Plc, comments on the widening of the
yuan’s trading band by the People’s Bank of China.  “The message of this move is that renminbi’s appreciation
story is over. Greater two-way volatility will be the name of
the game going forward.”  To contact the Bloomberg News staff on this story:
